Checklist for new releases
==========================

- [ ] update NEWS
- [ ] tag commit with new version number
- [ ] add `final` option to core_econometrics.tex and run Makefile to
  generate new pdfs (then turn off `final`)
- [ ] push to public repo (and --tags too)
- [ ] upload pdfs to 'releases' section on GitHub
- [ ] update version number and links to pdfs on index.md in gh-pages
      branch
- [ ] push gh-pages to public repo
- [ ] update version number and links to pdf on main homepage
- [ ] (optional) write blog post and email listserv
